overview:
Natalia is a Nationally Recognized Internet Dating Coach and online Media Mogul. After fifteen years of working in the private sector as a dating coach for women she teamed up with founder and CEO Colin Horwitz and launched the trend changing website eDateDoctors.com.

Raised in the culturally diverse city of Miami, Florida USA to Cuban-Jewish parents who were lawyers and psychologist respectively, she had the passion for helping others.After graduating from Miami University school of law she chose to follow her dreams of helping women. Instead of continuing in the profession of law she chose her true passion as a date coach for women.

With many years of helping A-List clients in the private sector such as doctors, lawyers, business moguls, and actors,She chose to continue and help out others in the capacity of public service instead of simply private.She took her expertise and experience and joined with other experts and formed eDateDoctors.com
